{"title":"PeFile","date":"2022-02-19T23:53:56.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年2月19日","L":"2022/02/19","MM-DD":"02-19"},"link":"2022/02/19/PeFile","tags":["PE"],"categories":["Reverse"],"updated":"2022-02-19T15:56:16.205Z","content":"<h2 id=\"pe文件格式\">PE文件格式<a title=\"#pe文件格式\" href=\"#pe文件格式\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>种类</th>\n<th>主扩展名</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>可执行文件</td>\n<td>EXE、SCR</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>库系列</td>\n<td>DLL、OCX、CPL、DRV</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>驱动程序系列</td>\n<td>SYS、VXD</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>对象文件系列</td>\n<td>OBJ</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><blockquote>\n<p><strong>OBJ</strong>以外PE文件都是可执行的，<strong>DLL</strong>、<strong>SYS</strong>文件等虽然不能直接在<strong>shell</strong>（<strong>Explorer.exe</strong>）中运行，但可以使用<strong>调试器</strong>、<strong>服务</strong>等执行</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"pe基本结构\">PE基本结构<a title=\"#pe基本结构\" href=\"#pe基本结构\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/PE1.jpg\" alt=\"PE1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/PE2.jpg\" alt=\"PE2\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/PE3.png\" alt=\"PE3\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"pe文件（windows-xp版本的32位notepad.exe）加载到内存中的情形\">PE文件（Windows XP版本的32位notepad.exe）加载到内存中的情形<a title=\"#pe文件（windows-xp版本的32位notepad.exe）加载到内存中的情形\" href=\"#pe文件（windows-xp版本的32位notepad.exe）加载到内存中的情形\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/IMG_20220218_195945_edit_125421789456903.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20220218_195945_edit_125421789456903\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"va&amp;rva\">VA&amp;RVA<a title=\"#va&amp;rva\" href=\"#va&amp;rva\"></a></h3>\n<p><strong>VA</strong>：进行虚拟内存的绝对地址</p>\n<p><strong>RVA</strong>（Relative）：相对虚拟地址</p>\n<p><strong>ImageBase</strong>：基准位置</p>\n<p><strong>VA与RVA换算关系</strong>：<br>\n$$<br>\nRVA+Image=VA<br>\n$$<br>\nPE文件内部信息多使用RVA表示，原因在于在多个PE文件（主要是DLL）调试加载时，如果使用VA就无法正常访问，而如果使用RVA，即使发生重定位基准位置发生变化，只要相对于基准位置的相对地址即RVA没有变化，就能正常访问</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>32位Windows OS中，各进程分配有4GB的虚拟内存，因此进程中VA范围为00000000~FFFFFFFF</p>\n<p>64位Windows OS中，各进程分配有256TB的虚拟内存，因此进程中VA范围为0000000000000000~FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"rva-to-raw\">RVA to RAW<a title=\"#rva-to-raw\" href=\"#rva-to-raw\"></a></h3>\n<p><strong>RVA</strong>（Relative Virtual Address ）：相对虚拟地址</p>\n<p><strong>RAW</strong> （FOA）：文件偏移</p>\n<p><strong>PointerToRawData</strong>：磁盘文件中节区所处地址</p>\n<p><strong>VirtualAddress</strong>：内存中节区所处地址<br>\n$$<br>\nRAW - PointerToRawData = RVA - VirtualAddress<br>\n$$</p>\n<p>$$<br>\nRAW = RVA - VritualAddress + PointerToRawData<br>\n$$</p>\n<p>使用上述公式时需要先根据地址找到对应所处节区再进行计算，不同节区<strong>PointerToRawData</strong>和<strong>VirtualAddress</strong>均不同</p>\n<h3 id=\"实例讲解\">实例讲解<a title=\"#实例讲解\" href=\"#实例讲解\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"pe头\">PE头<a title=\"#pe头\" href=\"#pe头\"></a></h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>以Windows10的Notepad.exe为例</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h5 id=\"dos头\">DOS头<a title=\"#dos头\" href=\"#dos头\"></a></h5>\n<p><code>struct IMAGE_DOS_HEADER DosHeader</code></p>\n<p>大小：64字节</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218201530515.png\" alt=\"image-20220218201530515\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218201954623.png\" alt=\"image-20220218201954623\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>文件最开始两个字节必为<code>4D 5A =&gt; &quot;MZ&quot;</code></p>\n<p>DOS头的2个重要成员：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">WORD e_magic   <span class=\"comment\">//即开头的MZSignature,DOS签名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">LONG e_lfanew  <span class=\"comment\">//即末尾的AddressOfNewExeHeader,表示NT头的偏移（可变），这里是F8h，所以NT头地址也为F8h，见下</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218202830144.png\" alt=\"image-20220218202830144\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"dos存根\">DOS存根<a title=\"#dos存根\" href=\"#dos存根\"></a></h5>\n<p><code>struct IMAGE_DOS_STUB DosStub</code></p>\n<p>大小：不固定</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218203631017.png\" alt=\"image-20220218203631017\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218203705256.png\" alt=\"image-20220218203705256\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>DOS存根同时保存着代码和数据，这里的代码非常简单，就是输出字符串“This program cannot be run in DOS mode.”，当notepad.exe文件在DOS模式下运行时（Windows 10下需借助DOSBox）会执行该操作</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218204333067.png\" alt=\"image-20220218204333067\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"nt头\">NT头<a title=\"#nt头\" href=\"#nt头\"></a></h5>\n<p><code>struct IMAGE_NT_HEADERS NtHeader</code></p>\n<p>大小：248（F8h）字节</p>\n<h6 id=\"第一个成员：签名\">第一个成员：签名<a title=\"#第一个成员：签名\" href=\"#第一个成员：签名\"></a></h6>\n<p><code>Signature</code></p>\n<p>其值必为50450000h（“PE”00）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218205154246.png\" alt=\"image-20220218205154246\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h6 id=\"文件头\">文件头<a title=\"#文件头\" href=\"#文件头\"></a></h6>\n<p><code>struct IMAGE_FILE_HEADER FileHeader</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218205007308.png\" alt=\"image-20220218205007308\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218210143844.png\" alt=\"image-20220218210143844\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218210901774.png\" alt=\"image-20220218210901774\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> _<span class=\"title\">IMAGE_FILE_HEADER</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    WORD Machine;    <span class=\"comment\">// 文件运行平台</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    WORD NumberOfSections;    <span class=\"comment\">// 区段数量,必须大于0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD TimeDateStamp;    <span class=\"comment\">// 文件创建时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD PointerToSymbolTable;    <span class=\"comment\">// 符号表偏移</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD NumberOfSymbols;    <span class=\"comment\">// 符号个数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    WORD SizeOfOptionalHeader;    <span class=\"comment\">//struct IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER64 OptionalHeader可选头大小，IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER32大小固定，IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER64和IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER32大小不同</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">FILE_CHARACTERISTICS</span> <span class=\"title\">Characteristics</span>;</span>    <span class=\"comment\">// PE文件属性</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_RELOCS_STRIPPED <span class=\"comment\">//Relocation info stripped from file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_EXECUTABLE_IMAGE <span class=\"comment\">//File is executable</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_LINE_NUMS_STRIPPED <span class=\"comment\">//Line nunbers stripped from file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_LOCAL_SYMS_STRIPPED <span class=\"comment\">//Local symbols stripped from file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_AGGRESIVE_WS_TRIM <span class=\"comment\">//Agressively trim working set</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_LARGE_ADDRESS_AWARE <span class=\"comment\">//App can handle &gt;2gb addresses</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_BYTES_REVERSED_LO <span class=\"comment\">//Bytes of machine word are reversed</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_32BIT_MACHINE <span class=\"comment\">//bit word machine</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_DEBUG_STRIPPED <span class=\"comment\">//Debugging info stripped from file in .DBG file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_REMOVABLE_RUN_FROM_SWAP <span class=\"comment\">//If Image is on removable media, copy and run from the swap file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_NET_RUN_FROM_SWAP <span class=\"comment\">//If Image is on Net, copy and run from the swap file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_SYSTEM <span class=\"comment\">//System File</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_DLL <span class=\"comment\">//File is a DLL</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_UP_SYSTEM_ONLY <span class=\"comment\">//File should only be run on a UP machine</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        WORD IMAGE_FILE_BYTES_REVERSED_HI <span class=\"comment\">//Bytes of machine word are reversed</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"可选头\">可选头<a title=\"#可选头\" href=\"#可选头\"></a></h6>\n<p><code>struct IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER64 OptionalHeader</code>是PE结构体中最大的</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218211354498.png\" alt=\"image-20220218211354498\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218211415748.png\" alt=\"image-20220218211415748\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><strong>重要成员介绍：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Magic</p>\n <figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER32:\t<span class=\"number\">0x10B</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER64:\t<span class=\"number\">0x20B</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>AddressOfEntryPoint(OEP)</p>\n<p>该值持有程序最先执行的代码起始地址（程序入口<strong>EP</strong>的<strong>RVA</strong>值）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>ImageBase</p>\n<p>ImageBase指出程序的优先装入地址</p>\n<p>在<strong>32</strong>位系统中，一般而言，<strong>EXE</strong>文件的<strong>ImageBase</strong>为<strong>00400000</strong>，<strong>DLL</strong>文件的<strong>ImageBase</strong>为<strong>10000000</strong></p>\n<p>执行PE文件时，PE装载器先创建进程，再将文件载入内存，然后把<strong>EIP</strong>值设为<strong>AddressOfEntryPoint+ImageBase</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>SectionAlignment,FileAlignment</p>\n<p>SectionAlignment指定节区在<strong>内存</strong>中最小单元</p>\n<p>FileAlignment指定节区在<strong>磁盘文件</strong>中最小单元</p>\n<p>两者可以相同</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>SizeOfImage</p>\n<p>指定PE加载到内存时所占空间大小，一般来说文件大小和加载到内存大小不同</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>SizeOfHeaders</p>\n<p>表示<strong>整个PE头</strong>的大小，必为<strong>FileAlignment</strong>的整数倍</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Subsystem</p>\n<p>用于区分系统驱动文件（ *.sys）和普通可执行文件（ *.exe, *.dll）</p>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">值</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">含义</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">备注</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Driver文件</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">系统驱动（如：ntfs.sys）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">GUI文件</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">窗口应用程序（如：notepad.exe）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">CUI文件</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">控制台应用程序（如：cmd.exe）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div></li>\n<li>\n<p>NumberOfRvaAndSizes</p>\n<p>用于指定DateDirectory数组个数</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>DateDirectory</p>\n<p>结构体数组，通常16个</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> _<span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD VirtualAddress;    <span class=\"comment\">// 数据表的起始虚拟地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD Size;    <span class=\"comment\">// 数据表大小</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;<span class=\"comment\">//DateDirectory结构体数组中每一个结构体都是这种格式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY_ARRAY</span> <span class=\"title\">DataDirArray</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">Export</span>\t//导出表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">Import</span>\t//导入表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">Resource</span>\t//资源表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">Exception</span>\t//异常处理表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">Security</span>\t//安全表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">BaseRelocationTable</span>\t//重定位表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">DebugDirectory</span>\t//调试表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">CopyrightOrArchitectureSpecificData</span>\t//版权</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">GlobalPtr</span>\t//指针目录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">TLSDirectory</span>\t//<span class=\"title\">TLS</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">LoadConfigurationDirectory</span>\t//载入配置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">BoundImportDirectory</span>\t//绑定输入目录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">ImportAddressTable</span>\t//导入地址表</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">DelayLoadImportDescriptors</span>\t//延迟载入</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">COMRuntimedescriptor</span>\t//<span class=\"title\">COM</span>信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY</span> <span class=\"title\">Reserved</span>\t</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h5 id=\"节区头\">节区头<a title=\"#节区头\" href=\"#节区头\"></a></h5>\n<p>为了保证程序的安全性，将PE文件创建成多个节区结构，将指令和数据等放在不同节区可避免其相互纠缠</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218214511832.png\" alt=\"image-20220218214511832\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218214548055.png\" alt=\"image-20220218214548055\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> _<span class=\"title\">IMAGE_SECTION_HEADER</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    BYTE    Name[IMAGE_SIZEOF_SHORT_NAME];\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 区段的名字，最长8字节，仅供参考，其值可任意修改，不能百分之百地被用作某种信息，甚至可以改成.tnnd</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">union</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            DWORD   PhysicalAddress;\t\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">            DWORD   VirtualSize;\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//内存中节区所占大小</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; Misc;\t\t\t\t\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD   VirtualAddress;\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 内存中节区所处地址RVA，VA=ImageBase+VirtualAddress</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD   SizeOfRawData;\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 磁盘文件中节区所占大小</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD   PointerToRawData;\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 磁盘文件中节区所处地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD   PointerToRelocations;\t\t\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD   PointerToLinenumbers;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    WORD    NumberOfRelocations;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    WORD    NumberOfLinenumbers;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">SECTION_CHARACTERISTICS</span> <span class=\"title\">Characteristics</span>\t\t\t//节区属性</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_TYPE_NO_PAD <span class=\"comment\">//Reserved</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_CNT_CODE <span class=\"comment\">//Section contains code</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_CNT_INITIALIZED_DATA <span class=\"comment\">//Section contains initialized data</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_CNT_UNINITIALIZED_DATA <span class=\"comment\">//Section contains uninitialized data</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_LNK_OTHER <span class=\"comment\">//Reserved</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_LNK_INFO <span class=\"comment\">//Section contains comments or some other type of information</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_LNK_REMOVE <span class=\"comment\">//Section contents will not become part of image</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_LNK_COMDAT <span class=\"comment\">//Section contents comdat</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_GPREL <span class=\"comment\">//Section content can be accessed relative to GP</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_16BIT </span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_LOCKED </span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_PRELOAD </span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_ALIGN_1BYTES </span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_ALIGN_2BYTES </span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_ALIGN_8BYTES </span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_ALIGN_128BYTES </span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_LNK_NRELOC_OVFL <span class=\"comment\">//Section contains extended relocations</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_DISCARDABLE <span class=\"comment\">//Section can be discarded.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_NOT_CACHED <span class=\"comment\">//Section is not cachable</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_NOT_PAGED <span class=\"comment\">//Section is not pageable.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_SHARED <span class=\"comment\">//Section is shareable</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_EXECUTE <span class=\"comment\">//Section is executable</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_READ <span class=\"comment\">//Section is readable</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ULONG IMAGE_SCN_MEM_WRITE <span class=\"comment\">//Section is writeable</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; IMAGE_SECTION_HEADER, *PIMAGE_SECTION_HEADER;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"iat\">IAT<a title=\"#iat\" href=\"#iat\"></a></h4>\n<p><code>Import Address Table</code>导入地址表</p>\n<h5 id=\"加载dll两种方式\">加载DLL两种方式<a title=\"#加载dll两种方式\" href=\"#加载dll两种方式\"></a></h5>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>显式链接（Explicit Linking）</p>\n<p>程序使用DLL时进行加载，使用完毕后释放内存</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>隐式链接（Implicit Linking）</p>\n<p>程序开始时即一同加载DLL，程序终止时再释放内存</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h5 id=\"调用dll函数方式\">调用DLL函数方式<a title=\"#调用dll函数方式\" href=\"#调用dll函数方式\"></a></h5>\n<p>调用DLL函数时并非直接调用，而是间接调用，因为相同函数再不同操作系统和不同语言中的地址可能不同，所以将地址直接放在IAT地址中，再进行调用，从而可以实现间接调用，还有一个原因在于重定位，如果直接调用的话，DLL原先的ImageBase可能会因为已经加载了运行程序的缘故重新定位，DLL会查找其他空白的内存空间，而使用间接调用就可以很好的解决问题，这就体现了IAT的作用了</p>\n<h5 id=\"image_import_descriptor\">IMAGE_IMPORT_DESCRIPTOR<a title=\"#image_import_descriptor\" href=\"#image_import_descriptor\"></a></h5>\n<p>该结构体中记录着PE文件要导入哪些库文件，有几个IMAGE_IMPORT_DESCRIPTOR就表示要导入多少库</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218233123006.png\" alt=\"image-20220218233123006\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> _<span class=\"title\">IMAGE_IMPORT_DESCRIPTOR</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">union</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD Characteristics;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    DWORD OriginalFirstThunk;<span class=\"comment\">//指向输入名称表的表（INT）的RVA，需计算RAW</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">DWORD TimeDateStamp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">DWORD ForwarderChain;</span><br><span class=\"line\">DWORD Name;<span class=\"comment\">//指向导入映像DLL文件的名称</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">DWORD FirstThunk;<span class=\"comment\">//指向输入地址表的表（IAT）的RVA,需计算RAW</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; IMAGE_IMPORT_DESCRIPTOR;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> _<span class=\"title\">IMAGE_THUNK_DATA32</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">union</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        PBYTE  ForwarderString;                                   <span class=\"comment\">//指向一个转向者字符串的RVA；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        PDWORD Function;      <span class=\"comment\">//被输入的函数的内存地址；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        DWORD Ordinal;       <span class=\"comment\">//被输入的API的序数值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        PIMAGE_IMPORT_BY_NAME  AddressOfData;      <span class=\"comment\">//指向IMAGE_IMPORT_BY_NAME</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; u1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; IMAGE_THUNK_DATA32;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> _<span class=\"title\">IMAGE_IMPORT_BY_NAME</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    WORD Hint;<span class=\"comment\">//ordinal</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    BYTE Name[<span class=\"number\">1</span>];<span class=\"comment\">//function name string</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; IMAGE_IMPORT_BY_NAME, *PIMAGE_IMPORT_BY_NAME;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218234135913.png\" alt=\"image-20220218234135913\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>INT和IAT大小应相同</p>\n<h5 id=\"pe装载器把导入函数输入至iat的顺序\">PE装载器把导入函数输入至IAT的顺序<a title=\"#pe装载器把导入函数输入至iat的顺序\" href=\"#pe装载器把导入函数输入至iat的顺序\"></a></h5>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>读取IID的Name成员，获取库名称字符串（eg：kernel32.dll）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>装载相应库：</p>\n<p>LoadLibrary(“kernel32.dll”)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>读取IID的OriginalFirstThunk成员，获取INT地址</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>逐一读取INT中数组的值，获取相应IMAGE_IMPORT_BY_NAME地址（RVA）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>使用IMAGE_IMPORT_BY_NAME的Hint（ordinal）或Name项，获取相应函数的起始地址：</p>\n<p>GetProcAddress(“GetCurrentThreadld”)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>读取IID的FirstThunk（IAT）成员，获得IAT地址</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>将上面获得的函数地址输入相应IAT数组值</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>重复以上步骤4～7，知道INT结束（遇到NULL）</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h5 id=\"notepad.exe文件导入表\">notepad.exe文件导入表<a title=\"#notepad.exe文件导入表\" href=\"#notepad.exe文件导入表\"></a></h5>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218234531841.png\" alt=\"image-20220218234531841\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">union</span> <span class=\"title\">DUMMYUNIONNAME</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  ULONG Characteristics:\t\t<span class=\"number\">190960</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  ULONG OriginalFirstThunk:\t<span class=\"number\">2E9</span>F0h\t.rdata FOA = <span class=\"number\">0x2DBF0</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">ULONG TimeDateStamp:\t\t\t <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ULONG ForwarderChain:\t\t\t <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ULONG Name:\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"number\">2F</span>846h\t.rdata RAW(FOA) = <span class=\"number\">0x2EA46</span> -&gt; KERNEL32.dll</span><br><span class=\"line\">ULONG FirstThunk:\t\t\t\t<span class=\"number\">278F</span>8h\t.rdata RAW(FOA) = <span class=\"number\">0x26AF8</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218235037922.png\" alt=\"image-20220218235037922\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>由此可知<code>2F846h</code>和<code>2F8F8h</code>都在.rdata节，所以根据</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218235157632.png\" alt=\"image-20220218235157632\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h6 id=\"计算并查看raw地址\">计算并查看RAW地址<a title=\"#计算并查看raw地址\" href=\"#计算并查看raw地址\"></a></h6>\n<p>OriginalFirstThunk.RAW = 2E9F0h+ 26200h - 27000h = 2DBF0h</p>\n<p>Name.RAW = 2F846h + 26200h - 27000h = 2EA46h</p>\n<p>FirstThunk.RAW = 278F8h+ 26200h - 27000h = 26AF8h</p>\n<p><strong>OriginalFirstThunk----INT</strong></p>\n<p>跳转到<code>2DBF0h</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218235643778.png\" alt=\"image-20220218235643778\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>可以得到<code>2F45Ch</code>，该区域认为**.rdata**节区然后计算RAW = 2F45Ch + 26200h - 27000h = 2E65C</p>\n<p>到<code>2 E65C</code>查看即可看到导入的API函数名称字符串</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220218235824883.png\" alt=\"image-20220218235824883\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><strong>Name</strong></p>\n<p>跳转到<code>2EA46h </code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219000022396.png\" alt=\"image-20220219000022396\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><strong>FirstThunk----IAT</strong></p>\n<p>跳转到<code>26AF8h</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219000207909.png\" alt=\"image-20220219000207909\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>这里即为IAT数组区域，对应于<code>KERNEL32.dll</code>库，和INT一样由结构体指针数组构成，以NULL结尾，这里的值和INT的一样，都指向了名称，在notepad.exe被加载到内存时，准确的地址值会取代该值，所以现在文件里的这些值意义不大</p>\n<h4 id=\"eat\">EAT<a title=\"#eat\" href=\"#eat\"></a></h4>\n<p><code>Export Address Table</code>导出地址表</p>\n<h5 id=\"kernel32.dll文件导出表\">kernel32.dll文件导出表<a title=\"#kernel32.dll文件导出表\" href=\"#kernel32.dll文件导出表\"></a></h5>\n<p>在NT可选头可以看到<code>IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY Export</code>信息</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219001802820.png\" alt=\"image-20220219001802820\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>可以看到相对内存地址的RVA为9A1E0h，由下图可知在.rdata节区内，所以可以计算出RAW</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219001817727.png\" alt=\"image-20220219001817727\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>RAW = 9A1E0h + 7EA00h - 80000h = 98BE0h</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219002253674.png\" alt=\"image-20220219002253674\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>下面对<code>IMAGE_EXPORT_DIRECTORY</code>结构体中的部分重要成员进行解释（全部地址均为RVA）：</p>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>项目</th>\n<th>含义</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>NumberOfFuctions</td>\n<td>实际Export函数的个数</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>NumberOFNames</td>\n<td>Export函数中具名的函数个数</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>AddressOfFunctions</td>\n<td>Export函数地址数组（数组元素个数=NumberOfFuctions）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>AddrssOfNames</td>\n<td>函数名称地址数组（数组元素个数=NumberOfNames）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>AddressOfNameOrdinals</td>\n<td>Ordinal地址数组（元素个数=NumberOfNames）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219002421642.png\" alt=\"image-20220219002421642\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>从库中获得函数地址的API为GetProcAddress()函数，该API引用EAT来获取指定API的地址。其过程大致如下：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>利用AddressOfName成员转到“函数名称数组”</li>\n<li>“函数名称数组”中存储着字符串地址，通过比较（strcmp）字符串，查找指定的函数名称（此时数组的索引称为name_index）</li>\n<li>利用AddressOfNameOrdinals成员，转到ordinal数组</li>\n<li>在ordinal数组中通过name_index查找相应ordinal值</li>\n<li>利用AddressOfFunctionis成员转到“函数地址数组”（EAT）</li>\n<li>在“函数地址数组”中将刚刚求得的ordinal用作数组索引，获得指定函数的起始地址</li>\n</ol>\n<p>kernel32.dll中所有到处函数均有相应名称，AddressOfNameOrdinals数组的值以index=ordinal的形式存在。但存在一部分dll中的导出函数没有名称，所以仅通过ordinal导出，从Ordinal值中减去IMAGE_EXPORT_DIRECTORY.Base 成员后得到一个值，使用该值作为“函数地址数组”的索引即可查找到相应函数的地址。</p>\n<h5 id=\"找kernel32.dll文件中的addatomw函数\">找kernel32.dll文件中的AddAtomW函数<a title=\"#找kernel32.dll文件中的addatomw函数\" href=\"#找kernel32.dll文件中的addatomw函数\"></a></h5>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219002725307.png\" alt=\"image-20220219002725307\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>首先找到<code>AddressOfNames</code></p>\n<p>计算RAW = 0x9A58C</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219002820746.png\" alt=\"image-20220219002820746\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>RVA = 9E1DFh</p>\n<p>计算RAW = 9CBDFh</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219003115482.png\" alt=\"image-20220219003115482\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>找到AddAtomW的index索引为7</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219003352450.png\" alt=\"image-20220219003352450\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>找到该函数的ordinal值</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219003441030.png\" alt=\"image-20220219003441030\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>所以ordinal值为7</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219003505542.png\" alt=\"image-20220219003505542\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>最后找到AddAtomW函数地址</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2022/02/19/PeFile/image-20220219003550156.png\" alt=\"image-20220219003550156\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>RVA = 25650h位于.text节区</p>\n<p>计算RWA = 25650h + 400h - 1000h = 24A50</p>\n<h2 id=\"各系统下最小的pe文件\">各系统下最小的PE文件<a title=\"#各系统下最小的pe文件\" href=\"#各系统下最小的pe文件\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Windows XP最小的PE文件：97字节</li>\n<li>Windows 2000上最小的PE文件：133字节</li>\n<li>通过 WebDAV 下载文件并执行的最小 PE 文件：133字节</li>\n<li>Windows 7 32位上最小的PE文件：252字节</li>\n<li>Windows 7 64位上最小的PE文件：252字节</li>\n<li>Windows 10上最小的PE文件：268字节</li>\n</ul>\n<p>97字节的PE文件生成可以看http://www.phreedom.org/research/tinype/</p>\n","next":{"title":"OsStart","link":"2022/01/28/OsStart"},"plink":"https://bexh0lder.github.io/2022/02/19/PeFile/","toc":[{"id":"pe文件格式","title":"PE文件格式","index":"1"},{"id":"pe基本结构","title":"PE基本结构","index":"2","children":[{"id":"pe文件（windows-xp版本的32位notepad.exe）加载到内存中的情形","title":"PE文件（Windows XP版本的32位notepad.exe）加载到内存中的情形","index":"2.1"},{"id":"va&rva","title":"VA&amp;RVA","index":"2.2"},{"id":"rva-to-raw","title":"RVA to RAW","index":"2.3"},{"id":"实例讲解","title":"实例讲解","index":"2.4"}]},{"id":"各系统下最小的pe文件","title":"各系统下最小的PE文件","index":"3"}],"copyright":{"custom":"转载请标明作者:D"},"reading_time":"3344 字约 22 分钟"}